    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Ok, I was missing some pieces, I thought there was only two cases. Makes sense with your explanation. Having a unified and maigical `autoHideContainer` options is also nice from our user POV, where we do not want them to dive too deep into the world of refinement and facets.\n\nLGTM, then\n",
